chapter 6:

culture and gene coevolve
in order to have the cultural evolution happen, gene had to select culture as a "traditional"  adaptive mechanism thus allow to evolution of culture taht in turn will promote the evolution of thing that will be adaptive \emph{within} pre-evovled cultural concept. The example of tribal instinct.


